<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="crazy-adj">crazy <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kreɪzi/    美 /'kreɪzi/  </p>
<p>[非正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>疯狂的；荒唐的；发狂的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is crazy of</strong> you <strong>to</strong> buy the car at such a high price.
以这么高的价钱买这辆汽车，你真是疯了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What a <strong>crazy idea</strong>!
这个想法真是荒唐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>went crazy</strong> with fear.
她害怕得发狂。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sound is <strong>driving me crazy</strong> (= really annoying me).
那种声音快让我发疯了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>狂热的；热衷的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>I’m crazy about</strong> football.
我很痴迷足球。</p></div></div>